sequenceDiagram
    participant Controller as KServe Controller
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Server as AutoGluon Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, 8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Factory as PredictorFactory<br/>(in-process)
    participant Predictor as AutoGluon Predictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant Client as Client / KServe Router
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Controller,Server: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup

    Controller->>Server: Create Pod<br/>(InferenceService CR)
    activate Server
    Server->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>kserve_storage.Storage.download()<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / storage-config
    Storage-->>Server: Model files (to local filesystem)
    Server->>Factory: Load model from directory
    Factory->>Factory: Auto-detect predictor type<br/>(try TimeSeriesPredictor first,<br/>fallback to TabularPredictor)
    Factory-->>Server: AutoGluonDetectedModel ready

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 2: v1 Tabular Inference

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext<br/>JSON payload: {"instances": [...]}
    activate Server
    Server->>Predictor: preprocess → DataFrame
    Predictor->>Predictor: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>or predict_proba()
    Predictor-->>Server: predictions array
    Server-->>Client: JSON response<br/>{"predictions": [...]}
    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 3: v2 Tensor Inference

    Client->>Server: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext<br/>InferRequest (tensor-per-feature)
    activate Server
    Server->>Predictor: preprocess → map tensors to DataFrame
    Predictor->>Predictor: TabularPredictor.predict()
    Predictor-->>Server: InferResponse (output tensors)
    Server-->>Client: InferResponse JSON
    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 4: v1 Time Series Inference

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext<br/>JSON: {"instances": [history],<br/>"known_covariates": [...]}
    activate Server
    Server->>Predictor: preprocess → TimeSeriesDataFrame
    Predictor->>Predictor: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()
    Predictor-->>Server: forecast DataFrame
    Server-->>Client: JSON response<br/>{"predictions": {...}}
    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 5: gRPC Inference

    Client->>Server: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/8081 plaintext<br/>InferRequest (protobuf)
    activate Server
    Server->>Predictor: preprocess → DataFrame
    Predictor->>Predictor: predict()
    Predictor-->>Server: InferResponse (protobuf)
    Server-->>Client: InferResponse
    deactivate Server

    Note over Prom,Server: Flow 6: Metrics Scrape

    Prom->>Server: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
    Server-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>request_preprocess_seconds<br/>request_predict_seconds<br/>request_postprocess_seconds<br/>request_explain_seconds

    deactivate Server
